headline: Two more U.S. power plants to be supported with long-term Wartsila service agreements
summary: Wartsila has signed a ten-year Long-Term Optimised Maintenance Agreement with Xcel Energy.The scope includes remote support from Wartsila's Expertise Centers, and all spare parts for the engines...
